    <h3>Conclusion: Visual Analysis and Insights on Phoenix's Solid Waste Production</h3>  
    <p>In 2021, Phoenix's total waste production was 1,423,023 tons, which was collected by curbside, bulk trash, or material hauled directly to the city's transfer stations before being transported to the Buckeye, AZ landfill.
